assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Winstar Display Co., Ltd. engages in the research, design, development, manufacture, and sale of industrial displays in Taiwan and internationally. Its products portfolio includes thin-film transistor (TFT) liquid crystal displays (LCDs), TFT displays, and TFT LCD modules; standard TFT color displays, TFT panels and controller boards, IPS TFT LCDs, HDMI signal TFT LCDs, high brightness TFT displays, bar type TFT LCDs, wide temperature TFT, monochrome TFT LCDs, and touch panels; and organic light-emitting diode (OLED) modules, passive matrix OLED, OLED display panels, and OLED dot matrix displays. The company also offers smart displays, TFT LCDs, and LCD screen panel modules; embedded motherboards, boards, and system boards; graphic LCDs and displays, character LCDs and display modules, chip-on-glass (COG) LCDs and displays, vertically aligned twisted nematic (VATN) LCDs and displays, and field sequential color (FSC) LCDs; and system integrated solutions. Its products are used in industrial machines, security systems, telecom products, white goods, audio systems, medical equipment, POS systems, cloud/IoT, intelligent technology, energy systems/equipment, wearable devices, smart home, and 3D printing applications. The company was founded in 1998 and is based in Taichung City, Taiwan.
